Class CCU825Packet

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.dz.ccu825.CCU825Packet
  • Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class CCU825Packet
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents CCU825-SM protocol packet. Does assembly/disassembly.

      • CCU825Packet

        public CCU825Packet(byte[] iData,
            byte[] key)
             throws CCU825CheckSumException,
                    CCU825PacketFormatException
        Construct packet object from raw protocol data received from ModBus IO transaction.
        Parameters:
        iData - What we've got from ModBus fn23
        key - Encryption key. See README.
        Throws:
        CCU825CheckSumException - If checksum does not match.
        CCU825PacketFormatException - If something is really wrong, like size or prefix.

      • CCU825Packet

        protected CCU825Packet(byte flags,

        Construct packet for transmission from flags byte and payload.
        Parameters:
        flags - - usually zero, except for handshake.
        payload - - data bytes to transmit.
